{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01EN2HsyAxHKrvjBjhkp8Ny3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The SQL connection is still timing out, but the internal logs show nodes are joining. The `cockroach node status` command uses the SQL/RPC port, not the HTTP port. The SQL connection is timing out.\n\nWait - from `crdb-cluster-0`'s container, when it tries to connect to `crdb-cluster-0.crdb-cluster.cockroachdb.svc.cluster.local:26257`, it seems to be timing out. But the HTTP health endpoint (`/health`) returns `{}`.\n\nLet me think about this. The HTTP port is 8080 and the SQL/RPC port is 26257. \n\nThe HTTP health endpoint is responding fine, but the SQL/RPC port is timing out. I'm wondering if CockroachDB is only listening on its own pod IP due to the `--advertise-host` setting, rather than all interfaces. By default it should listen on all interfaces, but maybe something's preventing that. I should check if the `--listen-addr` flag needs to be explicitly set, though in insecure mode it should default to listening everywhere. The issue might be that DNS resolution from within the pod to its own FQDN isn't working correctly.\n\nActually, looking at the `cockroach node status` error more carefully—\"failed to receive message (timeout: context deadline exceeded)\"—this suggests the TCP connection is actually being established but the gRPC message exchange is timing out. That's different from a connection refusal. The HTTP port works fine via curl, so the server is definitely running. Let me try connecting directly to the SQL port on localhost to see if that makes a difference.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":532,"cache_read_input_tokens":44766,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":532},"output_tokens":19,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01312bd2-5a74-4040-b24e-a9fadc515307","uuid":"cd2b5d58-42df-447d-9c97-2bd00cc65234","request_id":"req_011Cc87vr6fBYtUu3L1Lw5GY"}
